    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame1" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="4.4189in" svg:y="1.2055in" svg:width="1in" svg:height="0.4in" draw:z-index="280">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Fig. 1</text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame2" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="3.9189in" svg:y="0.8055in" svg:width="0.8in" svg:height="0.5in" draw:z-index="278">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="P4">Schermo ai fosfori</text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame3" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="2.4189in" svg:y="1.0055in" svg:width="0.9in" svg:height="0.4in" draw:z-index="277">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Materiale cristallino</text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame4" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="1.8189in" svg:y="0.9055in" svg:width="0.8in" svg:height="0.4in" draw:z-index="276">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Fascio di elettroni</text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame5" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="0.9189in" svg:y="0.8055in" svg:width="0.8in" svg:height="0.4in" draw:z-index="275">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="P5">Cannone elettronico</text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame>La figura 1 mostra uno schema di principio dell’esperimento. Abbiamo un fascio di elettroni che incide contro una sottile lamina di materiale cristallino, gli elettroni che attraversano la lamina vengono rilevati su uno schermo ai fosfori.</text:p>
