    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame18" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="-1.4693in" svg:y="1.3173in" svg:width="0.6in" svg:height="0.3in" draw:z-index="302">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="P4">6V</text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame19" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="-2.2382in" svg:y="0.9862in" svg:width="1.1in" svg:height="0.3in" draw:z-index="301">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:span text:style-name="T2">0 </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2"> 50V</text:span></text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame20" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="-0.8484in" svg:y="3.2571in" svg:width="0.9in" svg:height="0.4in" draw:z-index="305">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Fig. 10</text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame21" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="4.9189in" svg:y="1.1571in" svg:width="0.9in" svg:height="0.4in" draw:z-index="303">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="P9">Fig. 9</text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame>Gli alimentatori utilizzati sono due, uno per l’alta tensione di 0 <text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span> 5000kV ed uno per le basse tensioni di 6V e di 0 <text:span text:style-name="T4"></text:span> 50V. La foto in figura 10 mostra l’intero sistema alimentato. A sinistra c’è l’alimentatore ad <text:soft-page-break/>alta tensione, ed a destra l’alimentatore per le basse tensioni. L’ampolla è montata su un supporto universale.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2">Risultati sperimentali.</text:h>
