    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame22" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="2.4563in" svg:y="2.0161in" svg:width="0.9in" svg:height="0.4in" draw:z-index="309">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Fig. 11</text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame23" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="3.8791in" svg:y="1.0472in" svg:width="0.5in" svg:height="0.3in" draw:z-index="312">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="Standard"><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">2</text:span></text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame24" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="3.6835in" svg:y="1.1661in" svg:width="0.4in" svg:height="0.3in" draw:z-index="311">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="Standard"><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T6">1</text:span></text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr4" draw:name="Frame25" text:anchor-type="char" svg:x="5.8189in" svg:y="2.0181in" svg:width="0.8in" svg:height="0.4in" draw:z-index="310">
     <draw:text-box>
      <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Fig. 12</text:p>
     </draw:text-box>
    </draw:frame>La foto di figura 11 mostra in dettagli l’immagine ottenuta sullo schermo.<text:line-break/>Si osservano un punto centrale e due cerchi concentrici. La distribuzione di probabilità per la variabile <text:span text:style-name="T1"></text:span> che si deduce da quest’immagine è quella riportata in figura 12.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Se variamo la tensione di accelerazione si osserva che variano i raggi dei due cerchi, cioè variano gli angoli di deflessione <text:span text:style-name="T1"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">1</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T8"> </text:span>e <text:span text:style-name="T1"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">2</text:span>.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Sono state effettuate le seguenti misure:</text:p>
