       <semantics>
        <mrow>
         <mstyle mathsize="12pt">
          <mrow>
           <mi>ψ</mi>
           <mrow>
            <mo fence="true" form="prefix" stretchy="true">(</mo>
            <mrow>
             <mi>x</mi>
            </mrow>
            <mo fence="true" form="postfix" stretchy="true">)</mo>
           </mrow>
          </mrow>
         </mstyle>
         <mrow/>
        </mrow>
        <annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ψ left (x right )} {}</annotation>
       </semantics>
      </math>
     </draw:object><draw:image>
      <office:binary-data>AQAJAAAD7QAAAAIAFQAAAAAABQAAAAkCAAAAAAQAAAACAQEABQAAAAEC////AAQAAAAuARgA
       BQAAADECAQAAAAUAAAALAgAAAAAFAAAADAJgAqADEgAAACYGDwAaAP////8AABAAAADA////
       t////2ADAAAXAgAACwAAACYGDwAMAE1hdGhUeXBlAABgABAAAAD7Arz9CQEAAAAAkAEAAAAC
       BAIAEFN5bWJvbAACBAAAAC0BAAAIAAAAMgqeAXIBAQAAACgAEAAAAPsCvP0JAQAAAACQAQAA
       AAIEAgAQU3ltYm9sAAIEAAAALQEBAAQAAADwAQAACAAAADIKngH6AgEAAAApABUAAAD7AkD+
       AAAAAAAAkAEBAAAABAIAEFRpbWVzIE5ldyBSb21hbgAAoQQAAAAtAQAABAAAAPABAQAIAAAA
       MgqgARUCAQAAAHgAEAAAAPsCQP4AAAAAAACQAQEAAAIEAgAQU3ltYm9sAAIEAAAALQEBAAQA
       AADwAQAACAAAADIKoAH6/wEAAAB5AAoAAAAmBg8ACgD/////AQAAAAAAEAAAAPsCFAAJAAAA
       AAC8AgAAAAABAgIiU3lzdGVtAAAEAAAALQEAAAQAAADwAQEAAwAAAAAA
      </office:binary-data>
     </draw:image>
    </draw:frame><text:s/>è una distribuzione di ampiezze di probabilità e caratterizza lo stato della particella, questa funzione può essere vista come un vettore di infiniti numeri complessi e la rappresenteremo con il simbolo di vettore ket <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr15" draw:name="Object34" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.739in" svg:height="0.2055in" draw:z-index="22"><draw:object>
