      </office:binary-data>
     </draw:image>
    </draw:frame><text:s/>associato alla variabile posizione.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Per chiarezza ricapitoliamo i punti importanti di che abbiamo introdotto:</text:p>
   <text:list text:style-name="WW8Num8">
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P16">Una particella materiale è caratterizzata dalla variabile posizione, cioè da una coordinata che indicheremo brevemente con il simbolo <text:span text:style-name="T8">x</text:span>.</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P16">Lo stato di una particella materiale in un istante <text:span text:style-name="T8">t</text:span> è rappresentato dalla distribuzione di ampiezze di probabilità <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr15" draw:name="Object46" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.4791in" svg:height="0.2055in" draw:z-index="34"><draw:object>
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
         <semantics>
          <mrow>
           <mstyle mathsize="12pt">
            <mrow>
             <mi>ψ</mi>
             <mrow>
              <mo fence="true" form="prefix" stretchy="true">(</mo>
              <mrow>
               <mrow>
                <mi>x</mi>
                <mi>,</mi>
                <mi>t</mi>
               </mrow>
              </mrow>
              <mo fence="true" form="postfix" stretchy="true">)</mo>
             </mrow>
            </mrow>
           </mstyle>
           <mrow/>
          </mrow>
          <annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ψ left (x,t right )} {}</annotation>
         </semantics>
        </math>
       </draw:object><draw:image>
        <office:binary-data>AQAJAAADGgEAAAIAFQAAAAAABQAAAAkCAAAAAAQAAAACAQEABQAAAAEC////AAQAAAAuARgA
         BQAAADECAQAAAAUAAAALAgAAAAAFAAAADAJgAsAEEgAAACYGDwAaAP////8AABAAAADA////
         t////4AEAAAXAgAACwAAACYGDwAMAE1hdGhUeXBlAABgABAAAAD7Arz9CQEAAAAAkAEAAAAC
         BAIAEFN5bWJvbAACBAAAAC0BAAAIAAAAMgqeAXIBAQAAACgAEAAAAPsCvP0JAQAAAACQAQAA
         AAIEAgAQU3ltYm9sAAIEAAAALQEBAAQAAADwAQAACAAAADIKngEbBAEAAAApABUAAAD7AkD+
         AAAAAAAAkAEBAAAABAIAEFRpbWVzIE5ldyBSb21hbgAAgwQAAAAtAQAABAAAAPABAQAIAAAA
         MgqgAW4DAQAAAHQACAAAADIKoAEVAgEAAAB4ABUAAAD7AkD+AAAAAAAAkAEAAAAABAIAEFRp
         bWVzIE5ldyBSb21hbgAAgwQAAAAtAQEABAAAAPABAAAIAAAAMgqgAeACAQAAACwAEAAAAPsC
         QP4AAAAAAACQAQEAAAIEAgAQU3ltYm9sAAIEAAAALQEAAAQAAADwAQEACAAAADIKoAH6/wEA
         AAB5AAoAAAAmBg8ACgD/////AQAAAAAAEAAAAPsCFAAJAAAAAAC8AgAAAAABAgIiU3lzdGVt
         AAAEAAAALQEBAAQAAADwAQAAAwAAAAAA
        </office:binary-data>
       </draw:image>
      </draw:frame><text:s/>della variabile <text:span text:style-name="T8">x</text:span>, che indicheremo con il simbolo di ket <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr15" draw:name="Object47" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.322in" svg:height="0.1945in" draw:z-index="35"><draw:object>
        <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
         <semantics>
          <mrow>
           <mstyle mathsize="12pt">
            <mrow>
             <mo stretchy="false">|</mo>
             <mi mathvariant="italic">ψt</mi>
             <mo stretchy="false">⟩</mo>
            </mrow>
           </mstyle>
           <mrow/>
          </mrow>
          <annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ \lline ψt \rangle } {}</annotation>
         </semantics>
        </math>
       </draw:object><draw:image>
        <office:binary-data>AQAJAAAD2AAAAAMAFQAAAAAABQAAAAkCAAAAAAQAAAACAQEABQAAAAEC////AAQAAAAuARgA
         BQAAADECAQAAAAUAAAALAgAAAAAFAAAADAKgAgADEgAAACYGDwAaAP////8AABAAAADA////
         t////8ACAABXAgAACwAAACYGDwAMAE1hdGhUeXBlAABwAAkAAAD6AgAAEAAAAAAAAAAiAAQA
         AAAtAQAABQAAABQCSQBIAAUAAAATAlcCSAAFAAAAFAJJAD4CBQAAABMCUAGfAgUAAAAUAlAB
         nwIFAAAAEwJXAj4CFQAAAPsCQP4AAAAAAACQAQEAAAAEAgAQVGltZXMgTmV3IFJvbWFuAACr
         BAAAAC0BAQAIAAAAMgrAAY4BAQAAAHQAEAAAAPsCQP4AAAAAAACQAQEAAAIEAgAQU3ltYm9s
         AAIEAAAALQECAAQAAADwAQEACAAAADIKwAFaAAEAAAB5AAoAAAAmBg8ACgD/////AQAAAAAA
         EAAAAPsCFAAJAAAAAAC8AgAAAAABAgIiU3lzdGVtAAAEAAAALQEBAAQAAADwAQIAAwAAAAAA
        </office:binary-data>
       </draw:image>
      </draw:frame>.</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P16">L’evoluzione dello stato è descritta dalla seguente equazione:</text:p>
    </text:list-item>
   </text:list>
   <text:p text:style-name="P17"><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr15" draw:name="Object48" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="1.4228in" svg:height="0.2457in" draw:z-index="36"><draw:object>
