   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">L’operatore <text:span text:style-name="T8">X</text:span> così definito viene chiamato operatore posizione.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Calcoliamo ora la derivata <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr15" draw:name="Object139" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.4465in" svg:height="0.3953in" draw:z-index="127"><draw:object>
