   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Quest’ultima deve essere vera per ogni scelta di <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr15" draw:name="Object162" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.322in" svg:height="0.1945in" draw:z-index="150"><draw:object>
