   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Per la 2<text:span text:style-name="T12">a</text:span> i passaggi sono identici.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">La 3<text:span text:style-name="T12">a</text:span> e la 4<text:span text:style-name="T12">a</text:span> sono praticamente ovvie, è valgono per qualsiasi operatore <text:span text:style-name="T8">A</text:span> infatti</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P19"><draw:frame draw:style-name="fr15" draw:name="Object194" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="2.5827in" svg:height="0.2327in" draw:z-index="182"><draw:object>
