   <text:p text:style-name="Standard">Ricordando la relazione di De Broglie <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr15" draw:name="Object242" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.4264in" svg:height="0.1854in" draw:z-index="230"><draw:object>
      <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
       <semantics>
        <mrow>
         <mstyle mathsize="12pt">
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="italic">pλ</mi>
           <mo stretchy="false">=</mo>
           <mi>h</mi>
          </mrow>
         </mstyle>
         <mrow/>
        </mrow>
        <annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{pλ=h} {}</annotation>
       </semantics>
      </math>
     </draw:object><draw:image>
      <office:binary-data>AQAJAAAD1QAAAAIAFQAAAAAABQAAAAkCAAAAAAQAAAACAQEABQAAAAEC////AAQAAAAuARgA
       BQAAADECAQAAAAUAAAALAgAAAAAFAAAADAJAAkAFEgAAACYGDwAaAP////8AABAAAADA////
       1////wAFAAAXAgAACwAAACYGDwAMAE1hdGhUeXBlAABgABUAAAD7AkD+AAAAAAAAkAEBAAAA
       BAIAEFRpbWVzIE5ldyBSb21hbgAAzwQAAAAtAQAACAAAADIKgAEdBAEAAABoAAgAAAAyCoAB
       cQABAAAAcAAQAAAA+wJA/gAAAAAAAJABAAAAAgQCABBTeW1ib2wAAgQAAAAtAQEABAAAAPAB
       AAAIAAAAMgqAAcUCAQAAAD0AEAAAAPsCQP4AAAAAAACQAQEAAAIEAgAQU3ltYm9sAAIEAAAA
       LQEAAAQAAADwAQEACAAAADIKgAFRAQEAAABsAAoAAAAmBg8ACgD/////AQAAAAAAEAAAAPsC
       FAAJAAAAAAC8AgAAAAABAgIiU3lzdGVtAAAEAAAALQEBAAQAAADwAQAAAwAAAAAA
      </office:binary-data>
     </draw:image>
    </draw:frame><text:s/>possiamo concludere che deve essere <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr15" draw:name="Object243" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="1.4299in" svg:height="0.3953in" draw:z-index="231"><draw:object>
      <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
       <semantics>
        <mrow>
         <mstyle mathsize="12pt">
          <mrow>
           <mn>2</mn>
           <mi>π</mi>
           <mrow>
            <mstyle mathvariant="italic">
             <mtext>cm</mtext>
            </mstyle>
            <mo stretchy="false">=</mo>
            <mi>h</mi>
           </mrow>
           <mo stretchy="false">⇔</mo>
           <mrow>
            <mi>c</mi>
            <mo stretchy="false">=</mo>
            <mfrac>
             <mi>h</mi>
             <mrow>
              <mn>2</mn>
              <mi mathvariant="italic">πm</mi>
             </mrow>
            </mfrac>
           </mrow>
          </mrow>
         </mstyle>
         <mrow/>
        </mrow>
        <annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{2π ital &quot;cm&quot;=h dlrarrow c= {  {h}  over  {2πm} } } {}</annotation>
       </semantics>
      </math>
     </draw:object><draw:image>
      <office:binary-data>AQAJAAADSQEAAAMAFQAAAAAABQAAAAkCAAAAAAQAAAACAQEABQAAAAEC////AAQAAAAuARgA
       BQAAADECAQAAAAUAAAALAgAAAAAFAAAADAKABEAPEgAAACYGDwAaAP////8AABAAAADA////
       r////wAPAAAvBAAACwAAACYGDwAMAE1hdGhUeXBlAADgAAkAAAD6AgAAEAAAAAAAAAAiAAQA
       AAAtAQAABQAAABQCUAK7CwUAAAATAlAC4Q4VAAAA+wJA/gAAAAAAAJABAQAAAAQCABBUaW1l
       cyBOZXcgUm9tYW4AAJ0EAAAALQEBAAgAAAAyChwEjQ0BAAAAbQAIAAAAMgqoAeIMAQAAAGgA
       CAAAADIKwAIuCQEAAABjAAgAAAAyCsACswUBAAAAaAAIAAAAMgrAAvIBAgAAAGNtEAAAAPsC
       QP4AAAAAAACQAQEAAAIEAgAQU3ltYm9sAAIEAAAALQECAAQAAADwAQEACAAAADIKHASYDAEA
       AABwAAgAAAAyCsAC/QABAAAAcAAVAAAA+wJA/gAAAAAAAJABAAAAAAQCABBUaW1lcyBOZXcg
       Um9tYW4AAJ0EAAAALQEBAAQAAADwAQIACAAAADIKHATUCwEAAAAyAAgAAAAyCsACOQABAAAA
       MgAQAAAA+wJA/gAAAAAAAJABAAAAAgQCABBTeW1ib2wAAgQAAAAtAQIABAAAAPABAQAIAAAA
       MgrAAlwKAQAAAD0ACAAAADIKwAL2BgEAAADbAAgAAAAyCsACWwQBAAAAPQAKAAAAJgYPAAoA
       /////wEAAAAAABAAAAD7AhQACQAAAAAAvAIAAAAAAQICIlN5c3RlbQAABAAAAC0BAQAEAAAA
       8AECAAMAAAAAAA==
      </office:binary-data>
     </draw:image>
    </draw:frame>. Per comodità si definisce la costante di Planck ridotta <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr15" draw:name="Object244" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.4902in" svg:height="0.3953in" draw:z-index="232"><draw:object>
      <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
       <semantics>
        <mrow>
         <mstyle mathsize="12pt">
          <mrow>
           <mi mathvariant="normal">ℏ</mi>
           <mo stretchy="false">=</mo>
           <mfrac>
            <mi>h</mi>
            <mrow>
             <mn>2</mn>
             <mi>π</mi>
            </mrow>
           </mfrac>
          </mrow>
         </mstyle>
         <mrow/>
        </mrow>
        <annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ hbar = {  {h}  over  {2π} } } {}</annotation>
       </semantics>
      </math>
     </draw:object><draw:image>
      <office:binary-data>AQAJAAADKgEAAAMAFQAAAAAABQAAAAkCAAAAAAQAAAACAQEABQAAAAEC////AAQAAAAuARgA
       BQAAADECAQAAAAUAAAALAgAAAAAFAAAADAKABEAFEgAAACYGDwAaAP////8AABAAAADA////
       r////wAFAAAvBAAACwAAACYGDwAMAE1hdGhUeXBlAADgAAkAAAD6AgAAEAAAAAAAAAAiAAQA
       AAAtAQAABQAAABQCUALbAgUAAAATAlAC/gQQAAAA+wJA/gAAAAAAAJABAQAAAgQCABBTeW1i
       b2wAAgQAAAAtAQEACAAAADIKHAS4AwEAAABwABUAAAD7AkD+AAAAAAAAkAEAAAAABAIAEFRp
       bWVzIE5ldyBSb21hbgAAgwQAAAAtAQIABAAAAPABAQAIAAAAMgocBPQCAQAAADIAFQAAAPsC
       QP4AAAAAAACQAQEAAAAEAgAQVGltZXMgTmV3IFJvbWFuAACDBAAAAC0BAQAEAAAA8AECAAgA
       AAAyCqgBgAMBAAAAaAAQAAAA+wJA/gAAAAAAAJABAAAAAgQCABBTeW1ib2wAAgQAAAAtAQIA
       BAAAAPABAQAIAAAAMgrAAnwBAQAAAD0AEQAAAPsCQP4AAAAAAACQAQAAAAIEAgAQTVQgRXh0
       cmEAAgQAAAAtAQEABAAAAPABAgAIAAAAMgrAAjIAAQAAAGgACgAAACYGDwAKAP////8BAAAA
       AAAQAAAA+wIUAAkAAAAAALwCAAAAAAECAiJTeXN0ZW0AAAQAAAAtAQIABAAAAPABAQADAAAA
       AAA=
      </office:binary-data>
     </draw:image>
    </draw:frame><text:s/>con la quale scriviamo <draw:frame draw:style-name="fr15" draw:name="Object245" text:anchor-type="as-char" svg:width="0.402in" svg:height="0.3618in" draw:z-index="233"><draw:object>
      <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block">
       <semantics>
        <mrow>
         <mstyle mathsize="12pt">
          <mrow>
           <mi>c</mi>
           <mo stretchy="false">=</mo>
           <mfrac>
            <mi mathvariant="normal">ℏ</mi>
            <mi>m</mi>
           </mfrac>
          </mrow>
         </mstyle>
         <mrow/>
        </mrow>
        <annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{c= {  { hbar }  over  {m} } } {}</annotation>
       </semantics>
      </math>
     </draw:object><draw:image>
      <office:binary-data>AQAJAAAD7QAAAAMAFQAAAAAABQAAAAkCAAAAAAQAAAACAQEABQAAAAEC////AAQAAAAuARgA
       BQAAADECAQAAAAUAAAALAgAAAAAFAAAADAKABIAEEgAAACYGDwAaAP////8AABAAAADA////
       r////0AEAAAvBAAACwAAACYGDwAMAE1hdGhUeXBlAADgAAkAAAD6AgAAEAAAAAAAAAAiAAQA
       AAAtAQAABQAAABQCUAK/AgUAAAATAlACLAQVAAAA+wJA/gAAAAAAAJABAQAAAAQCABBUaW1l
       cyBOZXcgUm9tYW4AAKEEAAAALQEBAAgAAAAyChwE2AIBAAAAbQAIAAAAMgrAAjIAAQAAAGMA
       EQAAAPsCQP4AAAAAAACQAQAAAAIEAgAQTVQgRXh0cmEAAgQAAAAtAQIABAAAAPABAQAIAAAA
       MgqoAQIDAQAAAGgAEAAAAPsCQP4AAAAAAACQAQAAAAIEAgAQU3ltYm9sAAIEAAAALQEBAAQA
       AADwAQIACAAAADIKwAJgAQEAAAA9AAoAAAAmBg8ACgD/////AQAAAAAAEAAAAPsCFAAJAAAA
       AAC8AgAAAAABAgIiU3lzdGVtAAAEAAAALQECAAQAAADwAQEAAwAAAAAA
      </office:binary-data>
     </draw:image>
    </draw:frame>. Sostituendo questo valore possiamo finalmente dare l’equazione di Schrödinger nella forma definitiva</text:p>
